OL,3,CGary Lineker steps down from BBC and
OL,4,CMatch Of The Day after 25 years
OL,6,FAfter 25 years at the helm, Gary
OL,7,FLineker is set to step down from Match
OL,8,FOf The Day, as ITV News' John Ray
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FGary Lineker is to leave the BBC and
OL,12,Fis stepping down as the frontman of
OL,13,FMatch Of The Day, ITV News understands.
OL,15,FLineker, who turns 64 at the end of
OL,16,FNovember, is the highest-paid on-air
OL,17,Ftalent at the BBC and is under
OL,18,Fcontract until the end of the football
OL,19,Fseason.
