OL,3,CGary Lineker steps down from BBC and
OL,4,CMatch Of The Day after 25 years
OL,6,FHe was not offered a new contract for
OL,7,FMatch of the Day, the BBC reported.
OL,9,FThe news of Lineker's departure was
OL,10,Finitially reported in The Sun, with
OL,11,Fthe newspaper saying a BBC source told
OL,12,Fthem of his departure.
OL,14,FThe Mirror reported the same news
OL,15,Fearlier this year, citing an internal
OL,16,FBBC email that was allegedly leaked
OL,17,Fand suggested an announcement over his
OL,18,Fexit was being drawn up.
