OL,6,FThis was subsequently denied, with the
OL,7,Fcorporation suggesting discussions
OL,8,Fwere still ongoing over new terms.
OL,10,FLineker has previously laughed off the
OL,11,Fspeculation, joking that a Match of
OL,12,Fthe Day show in early October was his
OL,13,F"final" one, before adding: "before
OL,14,Fthe international break".
OL,16,FThe 63-year-old also oversees a
OL,17,Fsuccessful podcast business, which
OL,18,Fincludes the popular The Rest Is
OL,19,FFootball, which he hosts alongside
OL,20,FMatch Of The Day pundits Alan Shearer
OL,21,Fand Micah Richards.
