OL,3,CGary Lineker steps down from BBC and
OL,4,CMatch Of The Day after 25 years
OL,6,FThe former England, Tottenham and
OL,7,FBarcelona striker took over the BBC's
OL,8,Fflagship football highlights show in
OL,9,F1999 after predecessor Des Lynam
OL,10,Fjoined ITV.
OL,12,FLineker has been the BBC's highest-
OL,13,Fpaid on-air talent for seven
OL,14,Fconsecutive years and was estimated to
OL,15,Fhave earned #1.35 million in the year
OL,16,F2023/24, according to the
OL,17,Fcorporation's annual report published
OL,18,Fin July.
